(firstQuint)International Registry on the Quality of Life of Patients With Grass-pollen-induced Allergic Rhinitis.

 Primary objective: To describe the patient's perception of the impact of ORALAIR(R) on his/her health related generic and disease specific quality of life during the grass pollen season in real-life settings.

 Secondary objectives: - To describe the patient's perceived effectiveness of ORALAIR(R) in allergic rhinoconjunctivitis management in terms of disease intensity, satisfaction and rescue medication.

